snippet.title: Flux Caves - Trailer
snippet.description:
Just a short teaser trailer about Flux Caves 3d puzzle game
Download the Free Demo here: https://fubenalvo.itch.io/fluxcaves

Tha game is like mixing Portal, The Witness, Talos Prinicple and the good old Sokoban!
